			'''
	}

	Arpeggiator: {
		DisplayName: Arpeggiator
		Tooltip: Rapid-fires projectiles in an arpeggio pattern
	}

	ElementalReaper: {
		DisplayName: Elemental Reaper
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Spinning this scythe creates homing projectiles that inflict [rbuff:CalamityMod/ElementalMix]
			Press <right> to grant you and all allies one of the following Elemental Blessings for 10 seconds:
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheAirBuff]
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheBrimstoneBuff]
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheEarthBuff]
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheOasisBuff]
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheSandBuff]
			[rbuff:RagnarokMod/ScytheWaterBuff]
			'''
	}

	BrimScythe: {
		DisplayName: Brimscythe
		Tooltip:
			'''
			While spinning, you are surrounded in a circle of Brimstone Flames that deals constant damage
			Enemies hit by the circle are also afflicted by [cbuff:CalamityMod/BrimstoneFlames] for 5 seconds
			While below 25% hp, killing an enemy with the fire circle will heal you for 3 + 5% of the enemy maximum health
			'''
	}

	MaxEmpowermentTester: {
		DisplayName: Max Empowerment Tester
		Tooltip: Grants all empowerments at a level specified in item code :P
	}

	UnbreakableCombatUkulele: {
		DisplayName: Unbreakable Combat Ukulele
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Press <left> to play the ukulele
			Press <right> to throw the ukulele
			'Does not make for a good apology'
			'''
	}

	NightmareFreezer: {
		DisplayName: Nightmare Freezer
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Spinning the scythe periodically releases a barrage of chilling darts
			'Found somewhere between Halloween and Christmas... you could make a movie about that!'
			'''
	}

	DragonForce: {
		DisplayName: Dragon Force
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Consumes inspiration rapidly as you channel an inferno to your cursor
			Press <right> to play the [c/FF4500:Roar of the Jungle Dragon] riff!
			While the riff is active, the inferno this weapon unleases is amplified
			'''
	}

	Lamentation: {
		DisplayName: Lamentation
		Tooltip: Shoots homing brimstone gigablasts that inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/BrimstoneFlames] on hit
	}

	Virusprayer: {
		DisplayName: Virusprayer
		Tooltip: Shoots a barrage of acid bubbles
	}

	IntergelacticRobohelm: {
		DisplayName: Intergelactic Robohelm
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Increases symphonic damage, critical strike chance, and playing speed by 20%
			Increases inspiration regen by 15%
			Increases max inspiration by 6
			Increases empowerment duration by 3 seconds
			Reduces damage taken by 12%
			'''
	}

	IntergelacticRamhelm: {
		DisplayName: Intergelactic Ramhelm
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Decreases non-radiant damage by 40%
			Increases radiant damage by 30%
			Increases radiant critical strike chance and attack speed by 15%
			10% decreased mana usage
			+60 maximum mana
			Your healing spells will heal for an additional 5 life
			'''
	}

	KellyPet: {
		DisplayName: Wand of Anarchi
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Summons Kelly to follow you
			'Donor Item by HayWire799'
			'Sprites by Zenovia'
			'''
	}

	LeviathanHeart: {
		DisplayName: Leviathan Heart
		Tooltip: ""
	}

	SirenScale: {
		DisplayName: Siren Scale
		Tooltip:
			'''
			The Siren sings along with your enchanting tune.
			Symphonic damage increased by 15%
			Inspiration regen rate increased by 20%
			Anahita will sing along with your string instruments, firing additional water projectiles
			'''
	}

	ScourgesFrets: {
		DisplayName: Scourge's Frets
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Sends out bouncing sound waves that appear to be made out of sand
			Press <right> to play the [c/34C9EB:Guardian of the Former Seas] riff!
			While the riff is active, attacks from this guitar are twice as large and deal 25% more damage
			Time your attacks during the riff to reduce the cooldown
			'''
	}

	AuricGreatscythe: {
		DisplayName: Auric Greatscythe
		Tooltip:
			'''
			This scythe charges up the longer you spin it,
			accelerating to unbelievable speeds
			Press <right> to hurl a bolt of lightning
			'''
	}

	IrradiantInfinity: {
		DisplayName: Irradiant Infinity
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Press <left> to fire an [c/FF5555:Irradiant Red] orb with massive knockback
			Press <right> to summon an [c/55AAFF:Irradiant Blue] orb that follows your cursor
			[c/55AAFF:Irradiant Blue] pulls in nearby enemies and grows larger with each hit
			Once it reaches critical mass, strike it with [c/FF5555:Irradiant Red] to unleash [c/CC44FF:Irradiant Purple]
			'''
	}

	PrimalTerror: {
		DisplayName: Primal Terror
		Tooltip: Keep me favorited ;P
		HasAwoken: The Primordial Wyrm has awoken!
	}

	DevourerOfSines: {
		DisplayName: Devourer of Sines
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Channel this weapon to create a massive sine wave
			Press <right> to play the [c/501eb4:Universal Collapse] riff!
			While the riff is active, all players in range have unlimited flight
			'''
	}

	Ectambourine: {
		DisplayName: Ectambourine
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Throw an endless amount of ghostly tambourines
			Press <right> to jingle the thrown tambourines, damaging nearby enemies
			'''
	}

	InfectedOcarina: {
		DisplayName: Infected Ocarina
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Whistles out a cursed burst of noise
			Has a chance to shoot vile spit
			Press <right> to play the [c/50477e:Filthy Mind] riff!
			While the riff is active, infected pustules spawn around you
			Infected pustules will spew cursed fire at the nearest enemy
			'''
	}

	Shredder: {
		DisplayName: Shredder
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Sends out bloody shockwaves
			Press <right> to play the [c/AA1111:Blood Coagulant] riff!
			While the riff is active, all players in range have life steal
			Time your attacks during the riff to reduce the cooldown
			Missed timings during the riff do not reduce the cooldown, but also do not reduce your damage
			'''
	}

	SquirrelScarf: {
		DisplayName: Squirrel Scarf
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Increases your max number of sentries by 1
			'As fluffy as a squirrel's tail'
			'''
	}

	RiffTester: {
		DisplayName: Riff Tester
		Tooltip: Clears Riff Cooldowns. Use Responsibly.
	}

	StellarRiff: {
		DisplayName: Stellar Riff
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Sends out homing stars, that split into homing shards
			Playing success will increase the number of shards
			Press <right> to play the [c/00FFC8:Interstellar Stomper] riff!
			While the riff is active, stars rain down from above
			Homings shard count is doubled while the riff is active
			Time your attacks during the riff to reduce the cooldown
			'''
	}

	ToxicWaves: {
		DisplayName: Toxic Waves
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Launches floating toxic clouds that inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/SulphuricPoisoning] and [cbuff:CalamityMod/Irradiated] on hit
			The clouds will pierce through enemies based on your additional string weapon bounces
			Press <right> to play the [c/37C300:Toxic Wisdom] riff!
			While the riff is active, a sulphurous vortex summons acid sharkrons from above
			Time your attacks during the riff to reduce the cooldown
			'''
	}

	FateoftheGods: {
		DisplayName: Fate of the Gods
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Thanks to the entire team, everyone who supported, and those who all play the mod and keep it alive!
			The confines of this painting is not enough to fit the entire team
			[c/999999:Hold Left Shift to see a list of past and current developers]
			'''
		Donors: Donors
		Artists: Artists
		Programmers: Programmers
		OtherDevelopers: Other Developers
	}

	ProfanityFilter: {
		DisplayName: Profanity Filter
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Electronic weapons have 10% reduced damage, but 50% increased playing speed
			15% increased symphonic damage for weapons that are not Electronic
			10% increased symphonic critical chance
			Increases maximum inspiration by 4
			Symphonic damage has a 10% chance to increase the level of one of your active empowerments
			This effect can only trigger once every 2.5 seconds
			'''
	}

	RedglassMonocle: {
		DisplayName: Redglass Monocle
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Once worn by an infamous underworld star
			25% increased symphonic damage
			Flat Damage empowerment is twice as effective on you
			While worn, Radio Mic gets the following bonuses:
			Inspiration cost reduced by 2
			Increases the Damage empowerment level by 1
			Inflicts [rbuff:ThoriumMod/Charmed] for 5 seconds
			'''
	}

	RelicOfConvergenceOverride: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Creates a profaned crystal at the cursor that channels a healing aura before shattering
			All players within the area of effect are healed for {0} + 4x healing bonus HP
			Allies gain 50% extra healing
			Holding out the crystal decreases defense and increases incoming damage
			[c/FF8C00:Never once had I known kindness. Neither my peers or family had a shred of compassion for me.]
			[c/FF8C00:I wished for someone I could confide. A presence that cleansed me of anxiety.]
			[c/FF8C00:And when I saw Her radiant smile when we met, I knew I had finally found it.]
			'''
		DisplayName: Relic of Convergence
	}

	CorroslimeBass: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Sends out bouncing corroslime balls
			Press <right> to split balls into {0} smaller balls
			This process can be done {1} times
			'''
		DisplayName: Corroslime Bass
	}

	CrimslimeOboe: {
		DisplayName: Crimslime Oboe
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Shoots sticky crimslime darts
			After {0} seconds the darts will explode
			'''
	}

	StringsofOblivion: {
		DisplayName: Stringsof Oblivion
		Tooltip: ""
	}

	WulfrumGuitar: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Shoots bouncing sound waves
			Press <right> to return the waves
			Returning waves will ignore tiles
			'''
		DisplayName: Wulfrum Guitar
	}

	MenuMusicBox: {
		DisplayName: Music Box (Ragnarok Title)
		Tooltip: Plays 'Menu Theme' by CrafterDaemon
	}

	InspirationSingularity.DisplayName: Inspiration Singularity

	Asterion: {
		DisplayName: Asterion
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Creates a branching fractal of starlight around you
			This starlight occasionally grants you Starbursts on successful enemy hits
			Press <right> with enough Starbursts to create Asterion
			Asterion consumes Starburts quickly, but releases constant stellar pulses
			These pulses heal you and allies in range, and inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/Voidfrost] on enemies
			'As loyal as a hound'
			'''
	}

	FungalCastanets: {
		DisplayName: Fungal Castanets
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Alternating castanet clicks spray lingering fungal spores
			Press <right> to play the [c/00FFFF:1NF3S+@+!0N Riff!]
			During the riff, your castanets become Crabulon's claws while spores rain from above
			'Sounds like crab claws!'
			'''
	}

	CantStopWontStop: {
		DisplayName: Cant Stop Wont Stop
		Tooltip: This is the song that never ends...!
	}

	GlacialHarvester: {
		DisplayName: Glacial Harvester
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Hold <left> to spin the scythe
			Press <right> to slam the scythe, sending out a massive wave of ice
			Inflicts [rbuff:Frostburn]
			'''
		Cooldown: Glacial Slam is on cooldown
	}

	Aphelion: {
		DisplayName: Aphelion
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Hold <left> to spin the scythe, pulling nearby enemies into its vortex
			Spin long enough to summon two orbiting [c/DDEEFF:S][c/D2E3FA:t][c/C7D8F5:e][c/BCCDEF:l][c/B2C2EA:l][c/A7B7E5:a][c/9CACE0:r] [c/8697D5:M][c/7B8CD0:a][c/7181CB:s][c/6676C5:s][c/5B6BC0:e][c/5060BB:s]
			When both are active, press <right> to collapse their orbit into a supernova
			Inflicts [rbuff:CalamityMod/MiracleBlight] on hit
			[c/DDEEFF:S][c/D2E3FA:t][c/C7D8F5:e][c/BCCDEF:l][c/B2C2EA:l][c/A7B7E5:a][c/9CACE0:r] [c/8697D5:M][c/7B8CD0:a][c/7181CB:s][c/6676C5:s][c/5B6BC0:e][c/5060BB:s] inflict [rbuff:CalamityMod/Dragonfire], [rbuff:CalamityMod/GodSlayerInferno], and [rbuff:CalamityMod/Daybroken] on contact
			'''
	}

	Thaumonomicon: {
		DisplayName: Thaumonomicon
		Tooltip: ""
	}
}

